Mark grew up in Southeastern Connecticut amongst a diverse group of friends and family.  He experienced the comforts of mundane life early on, but he ultimately felt unsatisfied. On December 17, 2016, he had his first real awakening.  

Mark’s focus in teaching is to help you awaken to this same truth through the practice of insight meditation and to integrate these realizations in your daily life through the practice of loving-kindness meditation.  He truly believes that awakening is possible for anyone and everyone in this life and that it's the greatest gift you can give yourself and others.
